  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d2a86161-e089-4d37-95e0-0ebbeacb5777\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6ce3432f-ab3f-401e-8029-944d25dd275c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e044bb72-7c20-4788-aa78-6e0a335bfa9c\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 11</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a636e7c6-cf4d-4fe2-90b6-3633edc8bafd\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-271336de-a4a2-4c2d-bfcf-d28ea07fddc5\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bfddd1df-34b1-4e1f-bf0a-83b6612d4005\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-54ea1191-f191-4da5-975d-d17c1deb2992\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[11일 차 정리]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6150b119-8cf8-4397-b510-812e0c88a829\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6ea97d90-3978-4861-850e-dd07328bed9d\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>11일차를 맞이하여 지금까지의 작업을 정리하고 앞으로는 10일 간격으로 글을 체계적으로 업로드 할 내용을 미리 올리겠습니다. 아래 보이는 WBS는 앞으로 10일간 작성할 글 내용을 미리 업로드하여 알려 드릴것입니다. WBS는 나의 업무과업의 성과를 예측하고 목표까지 이상없이 작업하도록 하는데 의미가 있습니다. 약 90일 작성을 통해 (주)파파스컴퍼니 사이트의 개발 과정을 하나하나 되돌아 보실 수 있습니다.~</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-33d74b05-2b77-42dd-b1ad-98a35f643c84\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f0579772-110a-4997-96e2-95a19feaaa95\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-fb3e8e1b-3ce2-4081-be76-9070f0cd5ee1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3c8334f0-e479-41e9-b4e3-794f44102865\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5bfe395b-0bb1-425c-a5ed-b9a7fb17c5ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>네이버 블로그 WBS 작성을 통해 개발시 필요한 부분 정리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9cef9134-7b44-4c6b-8ea2-01d9c2d2a564\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-218f6dff-2d71-4da8-a6cc-a65a522269bb\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-138addcb-7b88-4add-a9ad-ddf42c087b3e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">네이버 블로그 글작성을 통해 WBS 문서를 만들어 봅니다. 본 WBS 엑셀파일을 원하시는 분은 아래 엑셀파일을 다운로드 받으시기 바랍니다. 앞으로는 더 디테일하게 보강하면서 문서작업까지 진행될 예정입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-51c4ac0a-cd26-444f-a273-c80b52c58f8d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9f12d7c4-3246-40a5-a2dc-90a0c15aa41c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-45414c9b-f633-447d-839c-5ea4ff295a81\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222891738424/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70a31672-ffac-4115-8258-d66cd80ab66a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b2b77b80-b6f6-429a-a293-6c31fa519d81\" style=\"\">블로그 작성에 대한 WBS</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-file se-l-default\" id=\"SE-102fb762-7713-4000-83cd-1c68a0a11fe9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-file se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-file\">\n<span class=\"se-file-icon\"><strong class=\"se-blind\">첨부파일</strong></span>\n<div class=\"se-file-name-container\">\n<span class=\"se-file-name\">카테고리 정리 220924</span><span class=\"se-file-extension\">.xlsx</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"se-file-save-button __se_link\" data-linktype=\"file\" href=\"https://download.blog.naver.com/open/ec79f04b506766d2f61f7a477195ea9f32679a27/EFsQb7ZKxLvO9d9aLuoSggWaFwbSq-dpeF8XKG00xEFxTtTRU3sg6Pe3C4Fogy8koyS4U0Pn2SE-yRdHWlzVE2EucFgKlJOBH132-nA/%EC%B9%B4%ED%85%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%20%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC%20220924.xlsx\" role=\"button\" target=\"_blank\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">파일 다운로드</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-83eca8ec-97c0-4a9f-82d9-c0353f76afae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-300aec92-90b4-4077-b887-493d214864c3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b771fb9a-e614-4a41-9c0e-b4bba10de5f0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 엑셀을 다운로드 하신다면 댓글이나 공감 한번 눌러주시는 것을 추천드립니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a10b8734-a93e-4285-adbe-076c0438eec6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-eb96ba82-2bd4-42f3-bc9d-9c30808ff091\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#ffffff;\">본 엑셀은 추후 계속 업그레이드 될 예정입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ac277504-74c8-4743-8351-8615884a7136\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7b3d4152-a5e5-45af-a787-85df40d7eaa9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-e4c392a2-09a1-44ba-a932-a08ce19d68cc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-213294cd-1065-4f7a-879b-625e225aebf6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5fb256e0-1cf3-4e4b-b3bb-62cfe646d674\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>주문 프로세스 정리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d611b177-6cff-4c53-942b-f79e53ff55b1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-df589140-c894-40e0-b126-449ab0ca1db7\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8b094065-a62f-4f57-9899-05d3a813bd91\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>디자인 선택​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2a3cc026-2f8f-4376-ad77-1f679ef99e62\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cc6cd15a-c133-46ea-9943-fe095c77a9d6\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 메인페이지에서 디자인템플릿을 선택하는 작업을 합니다. 이 부분에서 제일 중요한것은 검색 기능입니다. 자신의 입맛에 맞는 디자인을 빠르게 선택하기 위해 태그나 찜하기 또는 내가 주문한 템플릿을 먼저 보거나 관리하는 페이지가 있어야 합니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dc560b1f-a7a9-4fc4-8800-e9d8c85b801f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c42d226e-d81a-4f28-928e-71886a81233b\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">디자인을 빠르게 검토하거나 내가 자주하는 디자인템플릿 또는 선호하는 유형을 잘 관리하는 마이페이지 기능이 중요합니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9e553841-2633-4327-bd65-663ddfbec233\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-70dc1c2d-dc35-4362-8269-56b13f9de2b9\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">마이페이지에서 재주문을 가장 빠르게 다시 주문하도록 하는것이 관건입니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a51d21f2-ec0b-4801-9846-dddf8cd0827d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8e9f6945-97fb-4c49-85bc-d362254b8a89\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0a2a84fc-0433-4c39-9409-ef996674a0ae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222891738424/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22f4d3c3-e645-47dd-9b31-a8abbf5f8a51\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8c18e615-0b77-4389-8af1-bca062b0b6da\" style=\"\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 메인페이지</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-78002200-10da-4c11-adc3-472cca65d3c6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cfa5b5e2-e928-4ade-bd79-3d22a5846bc5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fe72c02c-5b2f-4d9f-858f-cd05ab0f91b1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4af2dedd-58ed-451c-ab26-d570be6cfbd3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:100px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222891738424/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-626a4c1a-1616-4e93-be4f-b415e36badb4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-92a8a05d-2873-42a2-9383-079c3b9bab14\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e3ec48b7-0132-49f7-b803-feab23e73759\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-23ddf3bd-31b6-4141-9bae-45bb6dd83739\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-770568d2-6261-4ec8-a082-07182cb9b745\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7d8570d6-46b8-4331-a032-06b3ad635f7c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e5c64639-4086-43f5-baaf-245178910e04\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>주문서 작성 페이지​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-efa1cd68-d613-45d4-9836-9ca8d00733e2\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e85a3170-a99b-4d93-889f-834dde259913\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">선택한 템플릿의 사양을 보고 변경하거나 추가로 요청할 페이지로 이동합니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-860a5443-8864-415e-95a9-b36d2e018e42\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ef62d760-c97d-4bfe-85c9-d4f8c2564713\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">요소의 변경은 템플릿이나 기타 디자인, 제품에 따라 다를 수 있습니다. 이 부분을 잘 정리하고 분류하는것이 주문할 때 빠르게 결정할 수 있는 초석이 됩니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4b8f19c1-e97e-4c21-93e6-e7f861cbb175\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6db71007-280a-46ab-ae95-3b2606d50081\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">우리는 자주하는 디자인 주문 또는 내가 관심있는 상품을 빠르게 검색하고 주문하는데 목적이 있습니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dbc63079-12e3-4c18-b084-531d9a055a5f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8b76ec82-c2be-4f65-9317-48b814f8bbf3\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b1b7f6b3-6ac7-4917-b145-eced400a7034\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222891738424/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5673bb65-08e1-4df1-8e39-9c05bdcdc575\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-26235d0b-dfd7-4e2a-8650-662cae9da63f\" style=\"\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 주문서 작성페이지</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3c34fdcb-2ee2-4096-af5b-d4dff5646308\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c58b5f2a-a96d-4444-b7e0-e1619fe7399a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c8f489ec-781a-44af-ba0c-5bad9697b42a\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5e597c2c-3ad3-4bea-a734-4c858bdedbc1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-45ed65e3-61a5-40f3-83b5-84e6fcb38aab\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e7d91d9b-5b52-478e-851d-69cf6d12230e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:100px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222891738424/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eda9929d-332b-4b3d-8372-88626a04e390\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3d52efa2-2a2a-4a96-9309-1cea25e75908\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-597b10a0-eb03-47f5-b172-350397b96124\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-77ac6d3e-3d85-45b3-9712-65ae2ee9522b\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3ec4923e-703b-4d81-b42d-25ff8ea0406f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>견적 확인 및 주문 페이지​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3bc9bf0a-bcd6-42e3-8ddd-02c324d54bac\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1b56896b-7ec6-4ac0-8223-bfb8fb9600ea\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">선택한 요소를 정리하고 내가 주문한 템플릿을 교정, 견적확인 및 결제의 과정을 관리하는 페이지입니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7a0809ea-a42e-4dff-b56f-d0c198d1106e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d30f7349-bafa-4597-bee0-52e2f0f1323e\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">내가 주문한 디자인과 제품의 최종 결정, 그리고 그 결제 및 납기등의 방법을 확인하고 통화하는 페이지입니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-45c1a663-3cfb-45fa-a7d2-0b01ce43cf08\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d4b7e447-c465-4c24-a34a-fa1c4b200896\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">자동을 마이페이지 상황의 커뮤니케이션은 생략합니다. 즉, 내 디자인의 수정과 제품의 생산과정의 프로세스를 다 넣고 관리하는 것은 너무 큰 작업입니다. 이 부분은 추후 자세히 설명드리겠습니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-aa839068-ff1c-405c-bfa8-cc9b1351dc80\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-32c5b5c5-d964-4766-95de-06dc73e1cd83\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3071deee-00a3-4a57-8e6f-4063d0a68b60\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222891738424/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-062b6622-48e1-46ca-a216-7b8a98f28105\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-53d44cab-0007-479f-9a41-5c10304e3b93\" style=\"\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 견적확인 창</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5af7f871-88c7-46b3-b812-74b8530e28af\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6b15b439-912b-4623-ac4c-0e18c2bac531\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-05ba7aba-16b7-4c70-bb69-56e3afa9742b\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c9bfcc1e-03f8-484b-9fdc-93c7d9c92c7e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-28854644-6f4d-42c1-9efc-2a395df40ed7\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 페이지는 추가로 설명항 부분이 있습니다. 추후 스토리보드 본작업시 설명을 추가하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1eb2da70-8331-463f-a4b1-5018ef959947\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5874eb64-a4c9-4144-bb4b-e78d8091763c\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a35354bd-b25e-4e9f-969c-74dae473c9cc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-310491f4-8e68-4b52-9158-6ce7c0201157\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-440af445-56a6-4247-90f4-86a1a7f69d28\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1ad3114d-521b-432c-8a2e-6d2eb1b1864c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-569425d1-ff0f-4316-8b34-08659f5e2d64\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>다음 글의 내용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-97d00d9a-c848-44a5-8495-24dc28d7543c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6393b1ce-9ef9-448c-9e7d-e9a3a3ea0d46\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f3e5350b-dfcf-4872-af19-4cb2830963a8\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[자료] </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cc7245b5-ec77-4418-8ada-875c1e76228e\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>요소 분석 [디자인]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a3b7baaa-c771-4496-afcb-fb109bab5be3\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-57cded35-9612-4712-9c87-051bedca7ccb\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0002f17c-8d06-4626-abb9-4e023f81f61f\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ca400167-992e-4943-aa58-99a57f53a57a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">세부 디테일한 설명을 이어갈 예정입니다. 디자인의 제일 큰 요소인 부분을 먼저 설명하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c2c6bfc8-f456-480f-8f51-92bfb8e641aa\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d7105c43-2ef7-4e5a-b5db-709dd0f12bc1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-143a3b12-a908-40ed-bbce-cd256e1d4c6d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:736px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222891738424/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f11686a4-ba40-427f-b8cf-01524fa7db1b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align